tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE TravelData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  travel_date DATE,
  origin_location VARCHAR(255),
  destination_location VARCHAR(255),
  travel_distance FLOAT,
  travel_duration TIME,
  passenger_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE historical_travel_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  source_location VARCHAR(50),
  destination_location VARCHAR(50),
  distance DECIMAL,
  travel_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE travel_predictions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  prediction_date DATE,
  source_location VARCHAR(50),
  destination_location VARCHAR(50),
  predicted_demand INT,
  optimization_strategy TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE historical_trips (
  trip_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  trip_date DATE,
  destination_city VARCHAR(255),
  trip_distance DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE TravelData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    traveler_name VARCHAR(50),
    travel_date DATE,
    origin_city VARCHAR(50),
    destination_city VARCHAR(50)
);
